        <p class="govuk-body">You usually need to do this within five days in England, although this does not apply if the death has been reported to the coroner.</p> 
        <p class="govuk-body">Registering a death may be different depending on where you live.</p>
        <p class="govuk-body">Your local registry office will have for more information on how to register the death.  You will need to book an appointment. </p>
